data.description: A Fantastic 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home w/ a main-level primary suite, located in the scenic Woodland Park area —just moments from shopping & close to I-40 for easy access to downtown, Blue Oval, & more. Recent updates (approx.) include a 2-year-old roof, 3-year-old HVAC (4 ton) & water heater, 1-year-old fence, & an upgraded breaker box. Features a split bedroom layout & lovely lake views from the upstairs bedrooms. $5k flooring allowance w/acceptable offer! Come see it today & make it yours.
